controls.label: wizard10
controls.customCode:
<button class="profileButton btn btn-primary"
        
  @click="function() {
    if (DonorPortal_GetCurrentUserWalletAddress() == null){
      if ($dgFormTouchSection()) {
        $dgFormGoToTab('Wallet')
          $setUser('profileSetUpStep', 2)
      }
    }
    if (DonorPortal_GetCurrentUserWalletAddress() != null){
      if ($dgFormTouchSection()) {
        $dgFormGoToTab('Top-Up Wallet')
          $setUser('profileSetUpStep', 3)
      }
    }
	}"        
        > 
Back
</button>
